Setting up new application on Rails

Install Ruby
Install Rails
Rails new appname
Rails server
Set Git version control	
	git config --global user.name myusername
	git config --global user.email myemail
	git init
	git status
	git add .
	git push

connect to heroku
deploy to heroku

create controllers
	para crear paginas automaticamente
	rails generate controller Pages home (controlador de paginas incluyendo home)

	
